      "annotated_filename": "Cranial_Meninges3_annot.jpg",
      "caption": "Coronal graphic shows the superior sagittal venous sinus as it is enclosed between the outer and inner dural layers. Arachnoid granulations project from the subarachnoid space into the superior sagittal sinus. Part of the brain's \"glymphatic system,\" meningeal lymphatics (schematically depicted in green) drain fluid from the interstitial fluid/CSF compartment to the deep cervical lymph nodes.",
      "image_path": "C:\\Users\\josem.000\\Documents\\repository\\Cranial_Meninges3.jpg",
      "annotated_path": "C:\\Users\\josem.000\\Documents\\repository\\Cranial_Meninges3_annot.jpg",
