      "annotated_filename": "Cranial_Meninges4_annot.jpg",
      "caption": "Graphic depicts an arachnoid granulation projecting into a dural venous sinus. A core of CSF extends from the subarachnoid space into the granulation and is covered by an apical cap of arachnoid cells. Channels extend through the cap to the sinus endothelium and drain CSF into the venous circulation. Note numerous trabeculae as well as small arteries and veins within the subarachnoid space over the brain.",
      "image_path": "C:\\Users\\josem.000\\Documents\\repository\\Cranial_Meninges4.jpg",
